evaluation.response:
It's not uncommon to experience negative self-thoughts around disappointment or perceived shortcomings.

As people age, it's natural to look back on life and reflect on how situations may have played out more in line with their values. An integral part of life, though, is the pursuit of resilience. Life is precious and worthwhile, even when it's imperfect.&#x20;

Feeling as you do today, it would likely be helpful to speak with a caring, informed person. You don't have to be laden with shame or self-loathing if sex hasn't felt as absorbing through this middle stage of adulthood as you hoped. Many people go through a 'sexual downturn,' so you are not alone.
